Khloe has been showing off her lean figure on the beaches of Turks and Caicos as she holidays with big sister Kim Kardashian and their kids. The 38-year-old TV star shares four-year-old daughter True with basketball player Tristan, 31 and her reps have now shared the happy news of baby number two with DailyMail.com. "We can confirm True will have a sibling who was conceived in November.” A representative for Khloe Kardashian told DailyMail.com. “Khloe is incredibly grateful to the extraordinary surrogate for such a beautiful blessing.".